## Typography

### Font Stack

**Headings & Brand Text**
```
font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', 'Consolas', monospace;
```
Monospace fonts evoke technical documentation, code, and maker culture.

**Body Text**
```
font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
```
Serif fonts for warmth and readability in long-form content.

**UI Elements**
```
font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
```
System fonts for buttons, navigation, labels — clean and fast-loading.

### Type Scale

| Element | Size | Weight | Font |
|---------|------|--------|------|
| H1 | 1.75rem | 700 | Georgia |
| H2 | 1.35rem | 700 | Georgia |
| H3 | 1.1rem | 700 | Georgia |
| Body | 1rem (17px) | 400 | Georgia |
| Small/Caption | 0.85rem | 400 | System UI |
| Code | 0.85rem | 400 | JetBrains Mono |

### Line Height

- Body text: `1.7` (generous for readability)
- Headings: `1.3`
- UI elements: `1.4`

