## Spacing System

Use consistent spacing based on a **4px base unit**:

| Name | Size | Usage |
|------|------|-------|
| xs | 0.25rem (4px) | Tight spacing, inline elements |
| sm | 0.5rem (8px) | Related elements |
| md | 1rem (16px) | Standard spacing |
| lg | 1.5rem (24px) | Section padding |
| xl | 2.5rem (40px) | Major sections |

### Content Width

- **Max content width**: 750px (articles, wiki pages)
- **Max card grid width**: 900px
- **Padding (mobile)**: 1.5rem
- **Padding (desktop)**: 2rem

