## Logo Usage

The CFL wordmark uses **JetBrains Mono Bold** in Ink color (`#2d2a26`).

**Clear Space**: Maintain padding equal to the height of the "C" on all sides.

**Minimum Size**: 100px width for digital, 1 inch for print.

**Don't:**
- Stretch or distort
- Add effects (shadows, gradients)
- Place on busy backgrounds without contrast

