## Accessibility

- **Contrast**: All text meets WCAG AA standards (4.5:1 minimum)
- **Font size**: Base 17px, never smaller than 14px
- **Link identification**: Underlines, not just color
- **Focus states**: Visible outlines on interactive elements
- **Alt text**: Required for all images

